<span id="freeTextContainer2084025698011548001"><b>*****5 SPARKLING PERFECT DOMINANT STARS!*****</b><br/><br/><b>
  <i>
    <blockquote>I wanted Brianna as I had wanted no other woman, and I couldn&apos;t have her. <br/>At least not yet. Soon though.</blockquote>
  </i>
